\section{A/V \& Lighting}

Technical support for our production will be handled on-site by:
\begin{itemize}[noitemsep]
    <% for person in config.technik.crew %>
    \item << person >>
    <% endfor %>
\end{itemize}

Our technical crew requires a Front of House (FOH) position in the house with a clear, unobstructed view of the stage.

\subsection*{Touring Equipment \& Tie-Ins}
We tour with the majority of our required technical equipment.
\begin{itemize}
    <% if config.technik.ton.aktiv %>
    \item \textbf{Audio:} We are carrying <% if config.technik.ton.mischpult %>our own FOH console and <% endif %> << config.technik.ton.anzahl_mikros >> wireless microphones. Our wireless systems operate in the 626--698 MHz RF band. We only require a \textbf{stereo line-level input (XLR or 1/4" TRS)} to tie into your House PA system.
    <% endif %>
    <% if config.technik.bild %>
    \item \textbf{Video/Projection:} We carry our own cameras and video switcher. We require an \textbf{HDMI drop} tying into your projection system or LED wall.
    <% endif %>
    
    <% if config.technik.licht.aktiv %>
    \item \textbf{Lighting:} We carry supplemental lighting fixtures<% if config.technik.licht.spot %> and a followspot<% endif %>.
    <% endif %>
\end{itemize}

